snippet.title: isabella's lullaby (The Promised Neverland lofi)
snippet.description:
isabella's lullaby but it's lofi.

it was supposed to be on YT earlier but it was immediately got a copyright claim so I had to tweak and change the key of the song. Hopefully it will avoid copyright claims.
EDIT - It was accepted but it's a Sharing Revenue (kinda disappointed). Also even ads are not available for Northern Mariana Islands, Nauru, New Zealand, U.S. Virgin Islands, Papua New Guinea, United States, Niue, Kiribati, Tonga, Samoa, Tokelau, U.S. Outlying Islands, Puerto Rico, Norfolk Island, Australia, Guam, American Samoa, Tuvalu, Vanuatu, Solomon Islands Viewers.
